milestones.description: Berrington and Calum MacLeod's 208-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 166 between Berrington and Calum MacLeod
Mohammad Nabi has become the top scorer for AFG in ODIs with 2122 runs, going past Shahzad's 2036
Berrington and Calum MacLeod's 208-run partnership is SCOT's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 203 between Fraser Watts and Hamilton
Calum MacLeod has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (98) in an innings in ODIs for SCOT, going past Kyle Coetzer's 92
Gulbadin Naib has broken the record for most ducks (5) in ODIs for AFG, going past Dawlat Zadran's 5
Kyle Coetzer has scored 14 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for SCOT breaking Berrington's record
